flowchart LR
    IN[prepared search state] --> DEC{intent == filter\nand shortlist exists?}

    DEC -->|yes| SKIP[search_embed skipped]
    DEC -->|no| EMB[search_embed]

    SKIP --> FILTER[search_hybrid:\nin-memory shortlist filters\n+ keyword ranking]
    EMB --> HYB[search_hybrid:\nprofile SQL + product SQL\nin parallel]

    HYB --> MERGE[merge by linkedin_slug\nsum RRF scores\nattach products]
    FILTER --> RR[rerank]
    MERGE --> RR[rerank]

    RR --> ENRICH[enrich_shortlist_light:\nformatted revenue]
    ENRICH --> OUT[shortlist for UI + summarize_search]
